rea requirement and is correct.\n- **Dependency versions are appropriate and compatible** `pyproject.toml:16`: fastapi>=0.100 and uvicorn>=0.23 are reasonable version constraints. Both libraries support Python 3.10+ as required by the project. No obvious conflicts with existing dependencies (typer, pydantic, pyyaml, questionary, slack-sdk). Versions are stable and well-maintained. No compatibility issues detected.\n",
